<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="353" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1357,1706]" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1357,1382]" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Differing from 
<taxonomicName box="[464,596,1357,1382]" class="Diplopoda" family="Aphelidesmidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="2" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Amplininae">Amplininae</taxonomicName>
in that the solenomere does not directly connect to the prefemur (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1915,1937]" captionTargetBox="[275,1327,204,1857]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[234,1368,196,1864]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Gonopodal configUrations of select aphelidesmine genera showing relatiVe lengths of the telopodital prefemora and acropodite. A. Aphelidesmus, A. junki GoloVatch, Hoffman &amp; Spelda, 2004, right gonopod, lateral View. B. Ochrotropis, O. guianensis (Chamberlin, 1923), left gonopod, lateral View (modified from Jeekel, 2000). C. Haematotropis, H. callipa (Peters, 1864), right gonopod, medial View. Scale lines: 1.00 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1439774/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">Figs. 2A–D</figureCitation>
; 
<figureCitation box="[234,307,1394,1418]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1949,1971]" captionTargetBox="[207,1386,185,1934]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[200,1394,180,1936]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 4. Gonopodal featUres of Xanthotropis media n. comb. A. Left gonopod, lateral View. B. The same, medial View. C. The same, dorsal View. D. Right gonopod, dorsal View (modified from GoloVatch et al., 2004). Scale lines: A–C (0.5 mm), D (1000 µm)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1439778/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">4A–D</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1357,1706]" box="[199,879,1429,1454]" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,357,1429,1454]" pageId="2" pageNumber="353">Components.</emphasis>
Four genera, distinguished in the ensuing key.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
